- Indeed.
- Come on.

859
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,360
Here you go.

860
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:03,640
A thirty-year-old bottle.

861
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,160
Great!

862
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,999
- Thank you!
- A thirty-year-old bottle.

863
00:34:05,999 --> 00:34:06,479
Just a sip.

864
00:34:06,479 --> 00:34:09,039
Mr. Shen is really bleeding money today.

865
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,400
It's 20 years old.

866
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,559
Fine, 20 years.

867
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,519
Okay.

868
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:16,599
It's rare to have
every single one of us together.

869
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,079
I think

870
00:34:18,720 --> 00:34:20,360
a family dinner should be at home.

871
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:21,920
It feels more meaningful.

872
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:23,440
Though a bit tiring

873
00:34:23,450 --> 00:34:25,240
for our head chef and sous chef.

874
00:34:25,240 --> 00:34:26,159
Tiring? Not at all.

875
00:34:26,159 --> 00:34:27,039
Thank you.

876
00:34:28,039 --> 00:34:29,679
I gathered everyone here

877
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,840
because

878
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:33,519
a lot of things happened to me.

879
00:34:33,519 --> 00:34:35,199
Things I never saw coming.

880
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:37,920
And I made you all worry.

881
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:41,559
I'm not strong enough

882
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:44,360
to handle everything on my own.

883
00:34:45,519 --> 00:34:47,360
Luckily, I had all of you by my side,

884
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:49,559
giving me so much love,

885
00:34:50,159 --> 00:34:51,079
and so much strength.

886
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,920
I'd like to thank all of you.

887
00:34:55,599 --> 00:34:56,920
Cheers.

888
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:57,720
Let's stand up.

889
00:34:57,960 --> 00:34:58,840
Okay, let's stand up.

890
00:34:58,840 --> 00:34:59,720
All of us?

891
00:35:00,119 --> 00:35:00,720
Okay.

892
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:02,519
Okay.

893
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:03,400
Alright.

894
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:06,720
Everyone, grab a seat.

895
00:35:06,720 --> 00:35:07,639
Grab a seat.

896
00:35:07,760 --> 00:35:08,320
Have a seat.

897
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:11,400
There's one more thing
I want to tell everyone.

898
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:13,400
My restaurant

899
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,519
has been acquired
by Manting Hotel Group.

900
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:19,199
They also invited me
to join their operations team

901
00:35:19,199 --> 00:35:20,679
after I have the baby.

902
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:22,920
And thank you

903
00:35:23,159 --> 00:35:24,840
for everything you did
to help the hotel.

904
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:26,240
Is it that Manting?

905
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:28,159
They must've paid a lot.

906
00:35:29,320 --> 00:35:30,639
We got our principal back.

907
00:35:30,639 --> 00:35:31,920
And even earned twenty grand.

908
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,720
You even made money!

909
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:34,320
Nice.

910
00:35:34,479 --> 00:35:35,280
That's great.

911
00:35:35,559 --> 00:35:36,800
It's great!

912
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:37,860
And there's one more thing.

913
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:39,599
Mom and Meiqi

914
00:35:39,599 --> 00:35:41,280
are starting a new business again.

915
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:41,880
Yes.

916
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:43,639
I fully support you two.

917
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:45,920
But I don't know anything
about your line of work.

918
00:35:46,119 --> 00:35:48,360
I won't get too involved, okay, Mom?

919
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:48,920
Alright.

920
00:35:48,920 --> 00:35:49,920
Come on, sit, sit.

921
00:35:50,639 --> 00:35:51,199
Okay.

922
00:35:51,679 --> 00:35:53,240
Thank you, thank you everyone.

923
00:35:53,240 --> 00:35:55,079
Look at all the things
our family's been through.

924
00:35:55,079 --> 00:35:56,280
Everyone stepped in to help.

925
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:57,240
Thank you.

926
00:35:58,880 --> 00:36:00,159
Let me say just a few words.

927
00:36:00,240 --> 00:36:01,159
Go ahead.

928
00:36:01,559 --> 00:36:02,320
Mingzhu.

929
00:36:03,039 --> 00:36:04,400
Once the baby is born,

930
00:36:04,599 --> 00:36:07,240
whether the child takes Feng, or Shen,

931
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:09,159
or Xu, or Yu,

932
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:11,400
none of that really matters.

933
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:12,920
What matters is

934
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,320
you're the mother.

935
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:18,039
All the rights over the child
are in your hands.

936
00:36:19,119 --> 00:36:19,760
And

937
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:21,679
I just hope from now on,

938
00:36:21,679 --> 00:36:23,400
you live by your own heart,

939
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:25,720
and live freely, however you want.

940
00:36:25,999 --> 00:36:27,920
As long as you're happy, that's enough.

941
00:36:29,240 --> 00:36:30,039
Thanks, Mom.

942
00:36:33,599 --> 00:36:34,920
Today I'm making the call.

943
00:36:35,519 --> 00:36:36,119
Bichen,

944
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:38,880
I'm giving you
this bracelet on Mom's behalf.

945
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:39,519
No, no...

946
00:36:39,519 --> 00:36:41,039
Mingzhu, that bracelet is yours.

947
00:36:41,039 --> 00:36:41,800
No, Mingzhu.

948
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:42,880
We can't take that.

949
00:36:43,840 --> 00:36:44,920
You didn't grow up

950
00:36:45,599 --> 00:36:47,320
at home with us when you were little.

951
00:36:47,370 --> 00:36:49,760
This is Mom making it up to you.
It's what you should have.

952
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:51,240
That's all in the past.

953
00:36:51,479 --> 00:36:52,760
We should look forward.

954
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:54,079
Besides,

955
00:36:54,679 --> 00:36:55,920
you said we're a family.

956
00:36:56,199 --> 00:36:57,880
This bracelet has to go to Bichen.

957
00:36:57,880 --> 00:36:58,920
Mingzhu, listen to me.

958
00:37:00,599 --> 00:37:01,639
You've moved past it.

959
00:37:01,639 --> 00:37:03,119
But the rest of us haven't.

960
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:05,559
We should be treating you twice as well.

961
00:37:05,559 --> 00:37:06,920
How could we take something

962
00:37:07,240 --> 00:37:08,519
this valuable from you?

963
00:37:09,159 --> 00:37:10,119
As for Chen,

964
00:37:10,559 --> 00:37:11,800
I'll buy her one later.

965
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:12,920
I can wait.

966
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:13,840
Zhidong,

967
00:37:14,519 --> 00:37:15,599
I'm your big sister.

968
00:37:16,159 --> 00:37:17,280
You need to listen to me.

969
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:19,360
This bracelet has to go to Bichen.

970
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:21,519
Ever since she married you,

971
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:23,760
she's put up with a lot.

972
00:37:24,599 --> 00:37:25,559
Consider this bracelet

973
00:37:25,920 --> 00:37:29,039
your family's love for her.

974
00:37:29,240 --> 00:37:29,760
Here.

975
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:31,840
No, Mingzhu.

976
00:37:32,599 --> 00:37:34,320
Dad, Mom.

977
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,280
Don't you think I'm right?

978
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:46,400
Madam Yu,

979
00:37:47,679 --> 00:37:48,679
she's talking to you.

980
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:49,999
Mom.

981
00:38:00,599 --> 00:38:01,199
Mom.

982
00:38:01,199 --> 00:38:02,400
She's asking for your opinion.

983
00:38:03,519 --> 00:38:05,840
Yes, she's right.

984
00:38:06,079 --> 00:38:06,880
Absolutely right.

985
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:07,679
Come on, Bichen.

986
00:38:11,620 --> 00:38:13,400
You two have to
treat each other well, okay?

987
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,240
Thank you, Mingzhu.

988
00:38:16,039 --> 00:38:17,079
Thank you, Mingzhu.

989
00:38:20,519 --> 00:38:21,240
Come on, sit.

990
00:38:25,079 --> 00:38:26,800
And lastly, I want to thank Mom and Dad.

991
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:28,400
Why're you thanking us?

992
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:29,710
- Yeah.
- After all these years,

993
00:38:30,079 --> 00:38:31,760
you two have done so much

994
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:32,920
for me and Minghui.

995
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:35,360
You barely had time to travel.

996
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:36,720
So now,

997
00:38:37,119 --> 00:38:39,679
before you officially
become grandparents,

998
00:38:40,519 --> 00:38:41,639
go home for a visit.

999
00:38:41,639 --> 00:38:42,639
No, you...

1000
00:38:42,639 --> 00:38:44,280
I already bought your plane tickets.

1001
00:38:44,519 --> 00:38:45,720
Just go and enjoy yourselves.

1002
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:47,400
Once the baby's here,

1003
00:38:48,050 --> 00:38:49,320
you can come back and help out.

1004
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,760
I covered half the tickets too.

1005
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:51,720
I've never

1006
00:38:51,720 --> 00:38:52,639
seen snow myself.

1007
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,559
Next time you go back,
you have to take me.

1008
00:38:56,119 --> 00:38:57,240
Okay, we'll take you.

1009
00:38:58,039 --> 00:38:58,639
Mingzhu,

1010
00:38:58,639 --> 00:38:59,720
let's toast Mom and Dad.

1011
00:39:00,240 --> 00:39:00,920
Mom, Dad,

1012
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:03,199
no matter what you decide to do,

1013
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:05,079
we're behind you.

1014
00:39:05,479 --> 00:39:06,159
My girl.

1015
00:39:07,530 --> 00:39:08,400
Thank you, sweetheart.

1016
00:39:10,599 --> 00:39:11,400
And me?

1017
00:39:11,599 --> 00:39:12,400
You too.

1018
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:14,119
But Mingzhu...

1019
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,559
Nothing to do with me now?

1020
00:39:16,720 --> 00:39:18,039
What about my part?

1021
00:39:19,119 --> 00:39:19,800
Sister.

1022
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,760
Wish you a smooth delivery.

1023
00:39:22,519 --> 00:39:23,800
Thanks, my little sister.

1024
00:39:24,599 --> 00:39:25,920
May all go smoothly.

1025
00:39:29,559 --> 00:39:30,679
Now that Mingzhu's done,

1026
00:39:31,720 --> 00:39:32,599
I'll say a few words.

1027
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:36,079
Today's a good day.

1028
00:39:36,720 --> 00:39:38,119
Thank you all for coming

1029
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:40,039
to my humble little place.

1030
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:43,400
We finally got everyone together.

1031
00:39:44,360 --> 00:39:45,240
Look.

1032
00:39:45,530 --> 00:39:46,880
"Brought together under one roof."

1033
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:48,800
This reunion

1034
00:39:50,119 --> 00:39:51,599
was brought to us by Mingzhu.

1035
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:53,400
If it weren't for her,

1036
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:56,920
I doubt we'd all be sitting here.

1037
00:39:58,039 --> 00:39:59,400
We're not technically one family,

1038
00:39:59,639 --> 00:40:00,920
but better than one.

1039
00:40:02,159 --> 00:40:03,079
There's an old saying,

1040
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:05,280
"If you're not family,
you might as well be one."

1041
00:40:05,639 --> 00:40:07,119
All these years, my wife and I

1042
00:40:08,240 --> 00:40:10,760
have been working our way
from the north down to the south.

1043
00:40:12,039 --> 00:40:13,400
It really wasn't easy.

1044
00:40:14,639 --> 00:40:16,599
Honestly, we're just ordinary people.

1045
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,519
All we ever wanted

1046
00:40:19,240 --> 00:40:20,639
was to live decent lives,

1047
00:40:21,079 --> 00:40:22,400
work hard, and stay honest.

1048
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:26,039
But in our hearts,
it was always our daughter first.

1049
00:40:26,599 --> 00:40:27,840
I'm grateful to our kids.

1050
00:40:28,599 --> 00:40:31,400
They taught us how to be parents.

1051
00:40:32,119 --> 00:40:34,280
Don't cry. Just hear me out.

1052
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:37,920
If this little home of ours can be okay,

1053
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:39,800
then all of us will be okay.

1054
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:42,400
I just hope every family here

1055
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,639
stays safe, healthy,

1056
00:40:44,999 --> 00:40:46,199
and happy.

1057
00:40:47,410 --> 00:40:48,800
Harmony makes everything flourish.

1058
00:40:50,079 --> 00:40:52,039
I'm not great with speeches.

1059
00:40:52,199 --> 00:40:53,720
Let me perform something instead.

1060
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:55,599
Alright, alright!

1061
00:40:56,199 --> 00:40:57,920
Minghui, help your dad out.

1062
00:40:58,760 --> 00:41:00,920
Jump in and back me up.

1063
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:02,159
That beat-boots thing you do.

1064
00:41:02,159 --> 00:41:03,559
Dad, it's beatbox.

1065
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:05,039
Drop the beat, right?

1066
00:41:05,039 --> 00:41:06,800
Drop the beat!

1067
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:07,320
Here we go.

1068
00:41:12,479 --> 00:41:16,519
Your mom says
I've always been a bit clueless.

1069
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:20,639
She says I'm carefree,

1070
00:41:20,639 --> 00:41:22,679
laughing all day,

1071
00:41:22,679 --> 00:41:24,760
scatterbrained and softhearted.

1072
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:29,039
Just a big silly fool.

1073
00:41:29,039 --> 00:41:30,079
A big fool.

1074
00:41:30,079 --> 00:41:31,159
A big fool, yep.

1075
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,400
Tell me this.

1076
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:36,320
If someone dropped
a gold ingot right on the street,

1077
00:41:36,559 --> 00:41:38,079
and it wasn't mine,

1078
00:41:38,079 --> 00:41:40,360
how could I take it?

1079
00:41:40,360 --> 00:41:41,039
Of course not!

1080
00:41:41,039 --> 00:41:44,760
If a whole hill bloomed
with golden chrysanthemums,

1081
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:46,360
and they weren't mine,

1082
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:48,599
why would I pick them?

1083
00:41:48,599 --> 00:41:50,559
I wouldn't!

1084
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:54,199
If golden radishes grew in the field,

1085
00:41:55,039 --> 00:41:56,559
and they weren't mine,

1086
00:41:56,559 --> 00:41:59,039
how could I pull them up?

1087
00:41:59,159 --> 00:42:02,720
If a gold frog jumped out of the river,

1088
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,840
and it wasn't mine,

1089
00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:06,880
why would I grab it?

1090
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:09,400
Gold ingot, gold flowers, gold radish...

1091
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:10,079
Jianqi.

1092
00:42:10,079 --> 00:42:10,880
Gold frog!

1093
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:12,639
Our family is finally here together.

1094
00:42:13,400 --> 00:42:14,199
And don't worry.

1095
00:42:14,679 --> 00:42:17,400
From now on,
we're all going to be just fine.

